```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DeviceDream Delights - Your Device Accessories Store</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to DeviceDream Delights</h1>
        <p>Your one-stop shop for premium device accessories.</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="featured-products">
            <h2>Featured Products</h2>
            <div class="product">
                <img src="product1.jpg" alt="Product 1">
                <h3>Phone Case</h3>
                <p>Protect your device in style with our durable phone cases.</p>
                <p class="price">$19.99</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <div class="product">
                <img src="product2.jpg" alt="Product 2">
                <h3>Screen Protector</h3>
                <p>Keep your screen safe from scratches and cracks.</p>
                <p class="price">$9.99</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more product listings here -->
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 DeviceDream Delights</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

In this template:

- The `<meta>` tags set character encoding and the viewport for responsive design.
- External styles are linked through `<link>` to a CSS file named "styles.css" for styling.
- The header contains the store's name and a brief description.
- Navigation links are provided in the `<nav>` element.
- Featured products are displayed in the main content area.
- Each product has an image, name, description, price, and an "Add to Cart" button.
- A footer with a copyright notice completes the template.

